            "body": "Just add the clusterId of the resourcemanager\u00a0in applicationId, it happens in rm, can't expose to client. Client do as before.\r\n\r\nIt will fix from the root.\r\n\r\nDefault applicationId is application_timestamp_xxx1, I will add `clusterId` after `application`, then the applicationId will be application_{color:#FF0000}clusterId{color}_timestamp_xxx1.\r\n\r\n\u00a0\r\n\r\n\u00a0",
